{"TopicId":159603,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Motorbike Design Challenge","CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T16:34:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T16:34:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I\u0027m a racing person. I\u0027ve got an entire\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Esave\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0file dedicated to racing. (I\u0027m thinking about starting a DMP server just for air racing). So I\u0027ve thought of something, and I\u0027ve decided to enlist your help. Your challenge: Design a vehicle that has 2 wheels (Or at least looks like it has 2 wheels), looks awesome, and can complete a lap around the test course.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(The test course)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022LWsMWLc.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/LWsMWLc.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou will be scored on these things;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFunctionality (It has to actually work)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks (You have to have that wow factor)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpeed (You can use the runway to test that)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgility (How fast can it turn those sharp hairpin turns?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd finally, time it takes the vehicle to complete 3 laps.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo in order for an entry to be official, it must have at least 4 pictures\u00A0(top-down picture, a picture from the side (I don\u0027t care which side), a rear picture, and a picture from the front), a front headlight, a rear brake-light\u00A0(Colored red for braking), and a\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ecommand seat\u003C/em\u003E. Drone cores are allowed to allow the bike to stop and let the crew on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRules confusing enough for ya? Good. Happy designing!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-22T19:35:01Z\u0022 title=\u002204/22/2017 07:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 22, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by DarkOwl57\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T16:35:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGive me a sec, I\u0027ll be back\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: parentheses now unecessary\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-22T16:53:07Z\u0022 title=\u002204/22/2017 04:53  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 22, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by qzgy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T16:39:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223030569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492878952\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160994\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022qzgy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, qzgy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Also, shouldn\u0027t this be in the challenges sub forum?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nidk\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex","CreatedById":75164,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T16:51:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI went ahead and did actually move this to Challenges, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161624-darkowl57/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161624\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161624-darkowl57/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@DarkOwl57\u003C/a\u003E, because it\u0027s set up exactly like a challenge is.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EI think I\u0027ll actually give it a go eventually.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T16:51:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223030596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492879872\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002275164\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tex\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Tex said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI went ahead and did actually move this to Challenges, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161624-darkowl57/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161624\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161624-darkowl57/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@DarkOwl57\u003C/a\u003E, because it\u0027s set up exactly like a challenge is.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nk; I was just confused\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NorthAmericanAviation","CreatedById":139039,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T19:07:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill probably give this a go, too. Also\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nCan I use jet engines as dead weight to shift the Center of Gravity below the ground? (makes the bike self-righting)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nWould it be a good idea to make \u003Cem\u003Ehow long it takes to run the test course\u003C/em\u003E one of the judging criteria?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd for everybody who will see this, \u003Cem\u003Emy \u003C/em\u003Eexperience has been that four wheels in sets of two clipped to look like one will provide better performance, given that rover wheels act like 2-dimensional discs. (correct me if I\u0027m wrong about this)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T19:34:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223030739\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492888050\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022139039\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NorthAmericanAviation\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, NorthAmericanAviation said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan I use jet engines as dead weight to shift the Center of Gravity below the ground? (makes the bike self-righting)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsure\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223030739\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492888050\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022139039\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NorthAmericanAviation\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, NorthAmericanAviation said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould it be a good idea to make \u003Cem\u003Ehow long it takes to run the test course\u003C/em\u003E one of the judging criteria?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew rule: You must test how long it takes to go around the track..... 3 times\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiffedStarfish","CreatedById":175356,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T19:39:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis sounds interesting, I\u0027ll definitely give it a shot tomorrow.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KenjiKrafts","CreatedById":175750,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-22T22:57:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n100% joining, I\u0027m a enthusiast irl so KSP is 100% xD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T03:05:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis was fun ... Here\u0027s my HOG driving down the runway hitting over 83m/s\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDone in my BDAc environment but fully stock with no part configs other than the Camo from DCK\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/347G-5BLxNk?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: 3 laps coming soon to a video near you\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-23T03:31:23Z\u0022 title=\u002204/23/2017 03:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 23, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by DoctorDavinci\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex","CreatedById":75164,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T05:00:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo Kerbals need to be in the seat(s) for the laps to count?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wanderfound","CreatedById":112611,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-24T05:33:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure if I\u0027ll have time to race, but an old bike for inspiration:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022screenshot1510_zps9kklnrxz.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i1378.photobucket.com/albums/ah120/craigmotbey/Kerbal/Beta/Kerbodyne%20Showroom/Kerbike/screenshot1510_zps9kklnrxz.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022screenshot1509_zpss7zzuh7u.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i1378.photobucket.com/albums/ah120/craigmotbey/Kerbal/Beta/Kerbodyne%20Showroom/Kerbike/screenshot1509_zpss7zzuh7u.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFour wheels for symmetry, but opposed and translated into each other to appear and function as two. Handles like a real bike; lean angle to turn, countersteering to hold the angle.\u00A0\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E just to pick it up again if you drop it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-24T05:34:01Z\u0022 title=\u002204/24/2017 05:34  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 24, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Wanderfound\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-24T12:38:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031348\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492923629\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002275164\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tex\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/23/2017 at 0:00 AM, Tex said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo Kerbals need to be in the seat(s) for the laps to count?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah. You could use a tweak scaled cockpit though\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223032514\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493012000\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022112611\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Wanderfound\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Wanderfound said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure if I\u0027ll have time to race, but an old bike for inspiration:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i1378.photobucket.com/albums/ah120/craigmotbey/Kerbal/Beta/Kerbodyne%20Showroom/Kerbike/screenshot1510_zps9kklnrxz.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022screenshot1510_zps9kklnrxz.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://i1378.photobucket.com/albums/ah120/craigmotbey/Kerbal/Beta/Kerbodyne%20Showroom/Kerbike/screenshot1510_zps9kklnrxz.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i1378.photobucket.com/albums/ah120/craigmotbey/Kerbal/Beta/Kerbodyne%20Showroom/Kerbike/screenshot1509_zpss7zzuh7u.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022screenshot1509_zpss7zzuh7u.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://i1378.photobucket.com/albums/ah120/craigmotbey/Kerbal/Beta/Kerbodyne%20Showroom/Kerbike/screenshot1509_zpss7zzuh7u.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFour wheels for symmetry, but opposed and translated into each other to appear and function as two. Handles like a real bike; lean angle to turn, countersteering to hold the angle.\u00A0\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E just to pick it up again if you drop it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wibou7","CreatedById":155221,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-25T20:49:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031235\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492916712\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150019\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DoctorDavinci\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2017-04-22 at 11:05 PM, DoctorDavinci said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis was fun ... Here\u0027s my HOG driving down the runway hitting over 83m/s\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDone in my BDAc environment but fully stock with no part configs other than the Camo from DCK\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/347G-5BLxNk?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: 3 laps coming soon to a video near you\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is awesome!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to see you do the race with that thing. And \u003Cstrong\u003EPLEASE\u003C/strong\u003E use \u0022Born to be wild\u0022 as the soundtrack \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}